Problem: Kernels are time consuming to develop as well as taking specialist knowledge to develop

Justification: This program will contain basic drivers for the specified architecture that the user wishes to output and will allow for faster and more optimal development for microprocessor / general OS development.

Idea 2:
Effects Of Quantum Computing within operating systems / embedded systems

Problem: We do not know a large amount on the effects that quantum computing will have within operating systems / embedded systems

Justification: To be a collection of knowledge and ongoing research of the effects as well as to explore the architectural changes that may need to occur in order to facilitate the system level programs for a quantum based machine.
